@1197 = ~Witherbranch~
@1198 = ~This cruel club appears to be nothing more than a gnarled, blackened bough, its surface split and twisted as if writhing in pain. It was cut from a tree deep within a plague-ridden grove, where Talona’s breath had stilled all life. Its thorns gleam with a dull green patina — residue from years of venomous anointing.

